creator: Quiply Technologies GmbH
descriptionHtml:
This app provides news and information about our company, products and services.

A great area where users can interactively get to know our company and interact with us.
• View current vacancies and send an inquiry if you are interested
• Get to know our values, way-of-business, passion projects and fun facts
• You saw a great photo motif of our organization? Take a picture and send it to us! If we find it also great and publish it, we will let you know.
• How well do you know our company? Take part in our quiz
• Find our nearest location to your current position on an interactive map
• Synchronize upcoming events with your calendar on your mobile device
descriptionShort: This app informs about what's happening within our company.
